# Project

This project is a premium dark fantasy trading card game interface called Legends of the Crypt.

## Core goal
Build a front end that feels like a high-end game client, not a generic React web app.

## Current stack
- React
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Tailwind
- Existing gameplay logic already exists
- Existing routing must not break

## Core principle
Preserve logic. Upgrade presentation.

## Never do these
- Do not rewrite game logic unless explicitly asked
- Do not break routing
- Do not rename major folders/files without reason
- Do not introduce random libraries unless clearly necessary
- Do not create generic SaaS-looking UI
- Do not clone external websites 1:1

## Priority order
1. UX clarity
2. AAA visual polish
3. Reusable components
4. Responsive layout
5. Clean TypeScript
